trans-unit.source: Provides a glyph for an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> to display when the activity it is associated with is set to read only at design time.
trans-unit.target: Gir et symbol for en <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref> skal vises når aktiviteten den er knyttet til er konfigurert til å lese bare under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ReadOnlyActivityGlyph"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ReadOnlyActivityGlyph"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns the bounds for the glyph on the specified <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer grensene for tegnet på den angitte <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> with which the glyph is associated.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref> med som tegnet er knyttet til.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to indicate whether the glyph appears on the activity designer surface; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>som viser om tegnet vises på utformingsoverflaten aktiviteten; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"></xref> that represents the bounds for the glyph.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"> </xref> som representerer grensene for tegnet.

trans-unit.source: designer contains a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: designerinneholder en nullreferanse ( i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Performs any tasks required to render the glyph on the activity designer surface.
trans-unit.target: Utfører en oppgaver som kreves for å vise tegnet på aktiviteten utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Drawing.Graphics"></xref> to perform fill and drawing tasks.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Drawing.Graphics"> </xref> til å utføre fyll og tegning oppgaver.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to indicate that the glyph appears on the design surface; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>for å angi at tegnet vises på utformingsoverflaten; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientTheme"></xref> to use to access ambient property settings.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientTheme"> </xref> skal brukes til å få tilgang til omkringliggende egenskapsinnstillingene.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> from which to obtain information about user actions.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref> som å få informasjon om brukerhandlinger.

trans-unit.source: Gets the priority setting for the glyph on the activity designer surface.
trans-unit.target: Henter prioritetsinnstillingen for tegnet på aktiviteten utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph.Priority%2A> always returns the integer value associated with <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph.LowestPriority?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph.Priority%2A>returnerer alltid heltallsverdi som er knyttet til <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph.LowestPriority?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph.LowestPriority?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph.Priority%2A>

trans-unit.target: En heltallsverdi som representerer prioritetsinnstillingen for den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ReadOnlyActivityGlyph"> </xref> på aktiviteten utformingsoverflaten.
